{"id":253,"parent_id":250,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":253,"title":"2 Peter 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Pet.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","Some in the latter days will doubt the Second Coming—The elements will melt at the coming of the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.1","order":"03.24.003.26202"},["b","1"],"This second epistle, beloved, I now",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"write"],"unto you; in",["i","both"],"which I stir up your pure minds by way of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"remembrance"],":"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.2","order":"03.24.003.26203"},["b","2"],"That ye may be mindful of the words which were spoken before by the holy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"prophets"],", and of the commandment of us the apostles of the Lord and Saviour:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.3","order":"03.24.003.26204"},["b","3"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Knowing"],"this first, that there shall come in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"last days"],"scoffers, walking after their own",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"lusts"],","],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.4","order":"03.24.003.26205"},["b","4"],"And saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Where"],"is the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"promise"],"of his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"coming"],"? for since the fathers fell asleep, all things continue as",["i","they were"],"from the beginning of the creation."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.5","order":"03.24.003.26206"},["b","5"],"For this they willingly are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"ignorant"],"of, that by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"word"],"of God the heavens were of old, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"earth"],"standing out of the water and in the water:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.6","order":"03.24.003.26207"},["b","6"],"Whereby the world that then was, being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"overflowed"],"with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"water"],", perished:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.7","order":"03.24.003.26208"},["b","7"],"But the heavens and the earth, which are now, by the same word are kept in store, reserved unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"fire"],"against the day of judgment and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"perdition"],"of ungodly men."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.8","order":"03.24.003.26209"},["b","8"],"But, beloved, be not ignorant of this one thing, that one day",["i","is"],"with the Lord as a thousand",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"years"],", and a thousand years as one day."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.9","order":"03.24.003.26210"},["b","9"],"The Lord is not slack concerning his promise, as some men count slackness; but is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"longsuffering"],"to us-ward, not willing that any should",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"perish"],", but that all should come to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"repentance"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.10","order":"03.24.003.26211"},["b","10"],"But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"day"],"of the Lord will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"come"],"as a thief in the night; in the which the heavens shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"pass away"],"with a great noise, and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"elements"],"shall melt with fervent heat, the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"earth"],"also and the works that are therein shall be burned up."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.11","order":"03.24.003.26212"},["b","11"],["i","Seeing"],"then",["i","that"],"all these things shall be dissolved, what",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"manner"],["i","of persons"],"ought ye to be in",["i","all"],"holy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"conversation"],"and godliness,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.12","order":"03.24.003.26213"},["b","12"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Looking"],"for and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"hasting"],"unto the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"coming"],"of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"day"],"of God, wherein the heavens being on fire shall be dissolved, and the elements shall melt with fervent heat?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.13","order":"03.24.003.26214"},["b","13"],"Nevertheless we, according to his promise, look for new",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"heavens"],"and a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"new"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"earth"],", wherein dwelleth",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.14","order":"03.24.003.26215"},["b","14"],"Wherefore, beloved, seeing that ye look for such things, be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"diligent"],"that ye may be found of him in peace, without",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"spot"],", and blameless."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.15","order":"03.24.003.26216"},["b","15"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"account"],["i","that"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"longsuffering"],"of our Lord",["i","is"],"salvation; even as our beloved brother Paul also according to the wisdom given unto him hath written unto you;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.16","order":"03.24.003.26217"},["b","16"],"As also in all",["i","his"],"epistles, speaking in them of these things; in which are some things hard to be understood, which they that are unlearned and unstable",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"wrest"],", as",["i","they do"],"also the other",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"scriptures"],", unto their own destruction."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.17","order":"03.24.003.26218"},["b","17"],"Ye therefore, beloved,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"seeing"],"ye know",["i","these things"],"before, beware lest ye also, being",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"led"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"away"],"with the error of the wicked, fall from your own",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"steadfastness"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.18","order":"03.24.003.26219"},["b","18"],"But grow in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"grace"],", and",["i","in"],"the knowledge of our Lord and Saviour Jesus Christ. To him",["i","be"],"glory both now and for ever. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.1a","order":"03.24.003.26220"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.1b","order":"03.24.003.26222"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.6.3-13"},"Alma 5:6 (3–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.2a","order":"03.24.003.26224"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/1.10"},"1 Pet. 1:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.3a","order":"03.24.003.26226"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-2-pet/3.3-13"},["span.small","JST"],"2 Pet. 3:3–13 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.3b","order":"03.24.003.26228"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"TG Last Days"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.3c","order":"03.24.003.26230"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/selfishness"},"Selfishness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.4a","order":"03.24.003.26232"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.26"},"D&C 45:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.4b","order":"03.24.003.26234"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.3.1-5"},"Matt. 16:3 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.4c","order":"03.24.003.26236"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/5.19.18-19"},"Isa. 5:19 (18–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.5a","order":"03.24.003.26238"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ignorance"},"TG Ignorance"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.5b","order":"03.24.003.26240"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-creator"},"TG Jesus Christ, Creator"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.5c","order":"03.24.003.26242"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/creation"},"TG Creation"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.6a","order":"03.24.003.26244"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/flood"},"TG Flood"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.6b","order":"03.24.003.26246"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/7.19"},"Gen. 7:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.7a","order":"03.24.003.26248"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-cleansing-of"},"TG Earth, Cleansing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.7b","order":"03.24.003.26250"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death-spiritual-second"},"TG Death, Spiritual, Second"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sons-of-perdition"},"Sons of Perdition"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.8a","order":"03.24.003.26252"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.8"},"Alma 40:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/3.4.4-9"},"Abr. 3:4 (4–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/time"},"TG Time"],"."],["div",{